Description:
A Podium Finish
This tranquil low rise home with leafy green views provides the ideal residence.
The award winning Watergate residence, with its eye catching Aero dynamic design, is a standout in the heart of the Docklands
With a uniformed layout, this larger than normal one bedroom apartment utilises every nook and cranny with it’s well designed floor plan.
As you step into this West facing apartment you will appreciate the stylish kitchen with white stone benchtop and white cabinetry. Integrated stainless steel appliances include a gas stove top, oven and a dishwasher.
Open plan dining and living area adjoins the full length balcony set along lush greenery.
Large bedroom with mirrored BIR’s adjoins the stylish fully tiled bathroom with dual access.
Additional features include ducted reverse cycle heating and cooling, secured carpark, onsite manager with security entrance, floor to ceiling double glazed windows and cross flow ventilation.
Recreational facilities consist of a fantastic 3 lane heated swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a residents lounge.
Centrally located in the heart of the Docklands makes it convenience plus. Walking distance to Woolworths, Australia Post Office, Library at the Dock, Southern Cross Station, superb cafes and eateries. Free Tram Zoned, easy access to the freeway and a short stroll into Melbourne.

Description:
Stunning Waterside Dimensions
Casting a striking silhouette in Victoria Harbour Precinct with absolute Yarra River frontage, this beautiful architecturally designed residence expands over four-levels to provide modern day convenience with panoramic views of the CBD skyline. Visually stunning design elements include versatile 3 bedroom + study/4th bedroom configurations plus parents retreat. The master domain with well appointed ensuite, walk in robe, balcony and fireplace. A Miele-fitted stone kitchen with adjoining living and dining flow to an entertainment courtyard with built in BBQ overlooking the river. Continue through the home to further fireside living room opening to a northerly terrace. Additional luxuries include a home theatre room, gym/studio, salt chlorinated lap-pool, 4 car basement garaging, an internal lift to all levels, reverse-cycle heating and cooling, cellar, under floor heating in kitchen, family room and all bathrooms, plus an abundance of storage. A special inclusion of a 23 metre marina berth.
This alluring waterside lifestyle includes easy access to amenities in and around the CBD. Reputable Primary and Secondary Schools are located in North Melbourne, South Melbourne, West Melbourne and surrounding areas. Melbourne University is accessible in the north of the CBD. RMIT University is located within the CBD also just a short distance to city department stores and boutique shopping, restaurants, bars and cultural precincts such as Chinatown (1km.) Further village shopping can be found in Port Melbourne, Albert Park or visit the South Melbourne Market, all just a few minutes away. With all entertainment venues in the CBD; Etihad Stadium, Rod Laver Arena, MCG, beaches in Port Melbourne, fine dining, Crown Casino, bike tracks and 15 minutes from the airport.
Insights: 60 South Wharf Drive, Docklands VIC 3008 was last sold in 2018 and 2 other 4 bedroom house in Docklands have recently been sold.

Description:
AFFORDABLE TWO BEDROOM APARTMENT!
Perfectly situated on the 23rd floor of the 'QUAYS' development is this magnificent two bedroom apartment with a huge balcony and incredible North Facing city views! This naturally light-filled apartment, with an abundance of sunlight in every room, is perfect for the first home owner or a smart investor.
Amenities include the Quays Health Club - complete with large gym, swimming pool and spa, rooftop garden with BBQs, club house and the first development in Docklands to feature a tennis court. There is also a Residents Lounge which includes boardroom facilities, cinema room and a private dining.
Be quick to grab yourself a slice of ta building design by MAB with award winning designs. Invest in a lifestyle with the convenience of cafes, restaurants, shopping and public transport at your leisure and you're only minutes away from Etihad Stadium and the CBD. Docklands is growing and is the place to be if you want a unique and vibrant lifestyle by the water.
For inspection call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235.

Description:
AMAZING OPPORTUNITY IN DOCKLANDS
Whether you are a first home buyer or an astute investor, don’t miss out on this incredible chance to buy in the Docklands. Located on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD sits the Lacrosse Building, ideally located next to Etihad Stadium, public transport, restaurants and shopping.
Currently returning approximately 6%, this 2 bed, 2 bath apartment has fantastic views of the CBD, includes a modern kitchen with stone bench tops and dishwasher, mirrored built in robes in the bedrooms, and clean, contemporary finishes in the bathrooms. A Euro-laundry and private balcony round out this well designed apartment.
This apartment is completed by split system heating & cooling, secure swipe and intercom entry, as well as use of the outdoor pool and gym. Whether you’re enjoying eating out with friends, swimming, shopping, or attending sporting events at Etihad Stadium, this is low maintenance living without the price tag.

Description:
Contemporary Pad in Vibrant Dockland Locale
Located in the heart of the thriving Docklands precinct, this delightful 2-bedroom apartment will undoubtedly win you over. Enjoying stunning views and showcasing a light-filled central living area, this 12th floor abode is moments to Etihad Stadium, Southern Cross Station, and Docklands bars and eateries.
Graced with gorgeous floor to ceiling windows and a fantastic sense of openness, this superb apartment ticks all the right boxes, highlighted by a bright central living zone with adjoining kitchen featuring sleek cabinets, concealed fridge, stylish splashback and quality stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher.
The private balcony is an amazing spot to enjoy the memorable harbour views with an afternoon beverage, while the master bedroom is robed and features a deluxe ensuite and shares in the glorious outlook. The 2nd bedroom is fitted with built-in robes, while the chic central bathroom has vogue shower tiles and a European laundry.
Further features include, a secure car space, split system heating & cooling, Euro laundry, intercom entry and communal facilities including gymnasium, sauna, swimming pool, BBQ area and cinema. An inspection is certain to impress!
Please note: inspection time may change or cancel without notice, please check the website before attending to inspection.
*Photo ID required at all open inspections

Description:
Immaculate Two Bedroom Apartment in Docklands
With a spot right in the heart of the sensational NewQuay Precinct, and showcasing an array of living highlights including modern luxury and a north-facing full-length balcony, this wonderful two bedroom apartment offers a lifestyle that is second to none.
This 8th floor retreat has everything you need for relaxed and stylish living. Fantastic central lounge and dining has sliding door access out to the large balcony where excellent views can be enjoyed over after dinner drinks and weekend meals. Back inside, a stone kitchen is fully equipped with stainless steel appliances and is perfect for those who love to cook from home.
Both bedrooms are equipped with mirrored built-in robes, meanwhile the bathroom has outstanding quality along with a concealed laundry. Also enjoy ducted heating and cooling, intercom entry, secure car space, and access to H1 facilities including a library lounge, media room, and gym.
Walk to the fabulous The District Docklands which has great restaurants and entertainment options, while you’re also close to terrific waterside restaurants, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, Etihad Stadium, IGA X-Press supermarket, and trams across Melbourne.
Please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 or Shaun Evans on 0488 488 379 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
UNDER OFFER - Rare Water Vistas in Elegant Single Bedroom
Perfectly placed in one of the Docklands most exclusive complexes, The Quays, this beautifully-appointed and relaxed single bedroom residence embodies modern apartment living that is sure to captivate CBD professionals, first home buyers and smart investors.
A formal entrance hall takes you directly into the central living and meals zone which boasts floor-to-ceiling windows and is an idyllic space to retire to at the end of a hard day at work. This hub further opens out to a balcony which features excellent south-westerly views and allows you an area to breathe in the fresh air and enjoy everything from summer BBQs to weekend wines on a Saturday night.
The designer kitchen is fitted with stainless steel appliances, while the bedroom with mirrored built-in robes has sliding doors allowing for an open or private experience. Also enjoy a stylish bathroom with vibrant mosaic wall tiles and European laundry, reverse cycle cooling, secure intercom and secure car space.
The sensational Quays complex offers a Health Club with a swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a yoga studio, while there is a Resident’s Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge. Further enjoy a rooftop garden with BBQ and dining facilities.
The NewQuay precinct is a lively hub and home to some of the Docklands best attractions. Trams will take you over all over Melbourne including the MCG, Richmond, Hawthorn and Box Hill, while surrounding restaurants cover cuisines of all types. You’re also moments from District Docklands, Medibank Icehouse, Costco, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel and the future Woolworths & Dan Murphies.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
AUCTION SATURDAY AUGUST 25 @ 10AM ONSITE
Delivering spectacular views, and a prime location, this large Lacrosse apartment on La Trobe Street.
Comprising of 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1 car space, this Docklands dwelling possesses space and elegance, as well as floor to ceiling windows that present a stunning vista of Melbourne.
The generous open plan living area comes with a stylish kitchen complete with dishwasher, stainless steel appliances, concealed fridge, and stone bench-top. The large master bedroom comes with built-in-robes, and a modern ensuite. The second bedroom is also generous in size, and includes plenty of storage with its built in robes. The central bathroom completes this prime property, with its clean, contemporary finishes, ample storage, and european laundry.
A feature throughout this inner city pad is loads of storage, and is rounded out by central heating/cooling, secure swipe and intercom entry.
Typical of modern apartment living, additional facilities for residents include a fully equipped gym and heated outdoor pool. With public transport, world class shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this must see apartment is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

Description:
A Docklands Jewel With Breathtaking Harbour Views
Taking ultra-modern, spacious, and stunningly bright Docklands living to a whole new level, this double storey two bedroom Victoria Point residence is a slice of the stylish good life. With remarkable views of Victoria Harbour, Port Phillip Bay, and Northern ranges, this 34th floor sensation is seconds to Etihad Stadium, local eateries, Docklands Park, trams, & Southern Cross Station.
Accommodation: Split over two light-filled levels, this apartment exudes contemporary class with stone and marble benchtops, bright full length windows, and great detail and quality fittings. The downstairs central living zone is an immense space allowing for airy lounge and dining areas, with this living space opening out to the balcony where the excellent south, west, and north views can be soaked in. The ground level also features a deluxe kitchen complete with stainless steel Miele appliances and a bathroom with European laundry, while upstairs has two large bedroom both with the amazing vistas including the master retreat which also has a large double vanity ensuite.
Features: 2 secure car space, storage, secure intercom & on-site building manager.

Description:
An unforgettable Forge offering with views to truly cherish
Brilliantly located in the luxury Forge residential complex which has an utterly peaceful Yarra’s Edge location, this resplendent 2 bedroom, 2 bedroom apartment displays phenomenal modern charisma and CBD views that are unforgettable.
This 7th floor apartment will melt your heart the second you step inside it. Bright full windows brings in sensational natural light throughout, while the magnificent views of the iconic CBD and Yarra River can best be enjoyed from the tranquil undercover balcony and master bedroom which comes with a built-in robe and chic ensuite.
The central lounge and dining hub promises an open playout and plenty of room to live and relax, meanwhile a gourmet stone kitchen comes with elegant cabinetry and stainless steel European appliances including a dishwasher. Other property highlights include a quality main bathroom, laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, and secure car space. You’ll also have access to the Wharf’s Club with gym, pool and café as well as a private kitchen/dining room and cinema.
This Yarra’s Edge location is well enough away from the action for residents to enjoy the quiet, while also still being close to terrific attractions including a variety of South Wharf promenade restaurants, DFO shopping, Port Melbourne and South Melbourne shops, lively Victoria Harbour precinct, and transport.

Description:
WISH UPON A STAR
This north facing superb two bedroom, two bathroom, luxury apartment gives views like no other from the 28th floor! This is the star of Convesso, comprising of two spacious bedrooms each with their own stylish bathroom, separate laundry room, a designer kitchen with stainless steel appliances, stone bench tops, and an abundance of cupboard space, living room with amazing water and Melbourne star views, a wide balcony perfect for entertaining, ducted air conditioning/heating and two secure undercover car spaces plus storage cage.
This 5 Star 'Convesso' building has set the bench-mark for all future living within the Docklands precinct. The views from this beautiful apartment could not be better as you peer from your living room or bedrooms across the water to NewQuay and beyond, the marina below or down the river to Bolte Bridge.
In addition, the amenities of this luxurious building includes:
- 24 hour concierge
- Residents Lounge
- Business Centre & Board Room
- Cinema (within the Concavo building)
- North facing Sky Garden facing the water, with BBQ facilities
- 25 metre indoor heated pool, spa and sauna
- Gymnasium and treatment room

Description:
Stunning space and views that will leave you breathless
Experience utter sophistication, magnificent space, and astounding 26th floor views in all directions with this flawless 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom residence, which has a place in the highly sought-after ‘Tower 3’ building in the Yarra’s Edge precinct.
You truly come for the views with this exceptional apartment, which has an enormous arched central living and dining zone which leads out to the huge balcony that curves all the way around much of the residence and enjoys magnificent vistas including the iconic CBD and Yarra River in all its glory.
The sumptuous kitchen will please home chefs and is complete with the finest quality stone and full stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, while just off the kitchen is a small sitting room which is ideal to take in the city at night. Four bedrooms in total is a rare find in Docklands properties, with the master bedroom the highlight of the lot that comes complete with a chic dual vanity ensuite and terrific BIR storage.
Two of the other bedrooms have access to their own private balcony which is south-facing, while further embrace a pristine bathroom, powder room, European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom entry, storage cage, and two car spaces, and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
In the most coveted location in the Docklands, you’re close to amazing South Wharf attractions including DFO shopping and restaurants and bars including The General Assembly, Plus 5 Bar, Meat Market, and The Boatbuilders Yard, You’re also near Crown Entertainment Complex, CBD attractions, and public transport including Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Price Reduced to Sell
Brilliant space, exemplary style, outstanding convenience.
With over 100 sqm (approx.) of fantastic internal living space and all the stylish modern features you’d expect from the excellent Watergate residential complex, this delightful three bedroom, two bathroom Docklands apartment is an amazing lifestyle opportunity.
Bright full windows lets in sensational light into the generous central lounge and dining zone, which is a large and tranquil place to eat and relax. A sizeable balcony is accessed via the living area and master bedroom, and has an easterly aspect which takes in views of Marvel Stadium. The gorgeous kitchen features a marble splashback and benchtop plus stainless steel appliances making it ideal to cook from home.
The master retreat boasts a study nook and private ensuite along with a built-in robe, while the other bedrooms with BIRs sit opposite the luxury central bathroom with laundry. Other highlights include central heating and cooling, intercom entry, 2 secure car spaces, and access to facilities including an onsite pool, sauna, and gym.
With easy access to both Victoria Harbour and Batman’s Hill precinct, you’re in close proximity to Marvel Stadium, Docklands Park, The Hub @ Docklands with outdoor sports facilities, local restaurants including The Hof Downtown and Twirled Pasta Bar, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
To arrange an exclusive viewing please contact Myles Johansson on 0448 031 716.

Description:
Stunning harbour views!
Maximising space and blue-water harbour views from every angle, this brilliantly bright 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom corner apartment takes luxury living to the next level.
Take advantage of oversized, open-concept living/dining framed by floor-to-ceiling glass, and a sleek, stone-topped kitchen with imposing, waterfall-edged breakfast bar.
Step outside and the apartment truly comes alive with a sheltered, full-width balcony showcasing uninterrupted Victoria Harbour views, the perfect backdrop for entertaining.
• 2 large bedrooms with mirrored BIR, main with stunning, fully tiled ensuite
• Roomy study nook with stylish built-in desk
• Deluxe, fully tiled bathroom plus concealed laundry and storage
• Ducted heating and cooling
• Roller blinds and freshly painted
• Secure undercover parking plus storage cage
• Lifestyle facilities include a fully fitted gym, media room and a library
• An impressive 92m2 internal and 15m2 external (both approx.)
On the city’s edge and metres from New Quay restaurants, you could not wish for a better address. This is prestigious Docklands living with all the benefits!
For more information, please contact Anthony Inglese today.

Description:
Huge stamp duty savings!
If you purchase this brand new magnificent north facing apartment you will be surrounded by the peacefulness of nature. Lush plant life cascades around the building exterior, a rooftop garden provides fantastic views and moments of tranquillity. Balconies with planters offer private gardens..
The apartment layout provides flexible living options. Unique loft apartment is bright and airy with expansive windows and 4.5 metre high ceilings, residents can use their imagination and transform the additional mezzanine area into anything from a studio to a hobby room, kids' play area or guest retreat.
Resident facilities within the building include, private meeting rooms, swimming pool, spa & sauna, gym.
A short stroll or walk to Harbour town shopping centre, restaurants and cafes on the waterfront, a short tram ride into Melbourne CBD and the iconic Melbourne star wheel.
The apartment features
• 2 bedrooms with BIR's plus a great size loft area which can easily be converted to a 3rd bedroom
• Internal area: 101.5m2

• One car park space
